abstract: Egyptian military announces security forces killed at least five Sudanese migrants who attempted to cross over Egyptian border into Israel.
lead_paragraph: The deaths came eight days after Egyptian border guards were accused in the fatal shootings of at least 15 Sudanese migrants trying to cross the frontier.
